data.description: Welcome to 26406 Clear Mill Lane in the Pine Mill Ranch community. Come inside this beautiful 2 story home & find 4 bedrooms, 2 full & 1 half baths, & a 2 car garage. The formal dining room has chair rail detailing & crown molding. Your kitchen has a raised breakfast bar, granite counters, SS appliances, gas range, pantry, & breakfast area. The living room has high ceilings, cast stone fireplace w/mantle, & lots of windows letting in natural light. Head to the primary suite & find a private ensuite bath with separate shower & bathtub, dual sinks, vanity, & a big walk-in closet with wood floors. Upstairs find 3 additional bedrooms, a big game room, & a full bath with dual sinks & shower. Your back yard has a large patio perfect for entertaining. The Pine Mill Ranch neighborhood offers many amenities to its residents including a community pool, clubhouse, volleyball courts, splash pad, catch & release fishing lake, & many green belts & walking trails.
